dcterms:description: FB15K is a subset of Freebase, containing around 15,000 entities with 1,345 different predicates in the form of knowledge base relation triples. The pageviews of Wikipedia pages are taken as the node importance.
dcterms:title: FB15K

dcterms:description: TMDB5K is a movie knowledge graph generated from the TMDB 5000 dataset, including around 5,000 movie entities as well as other entities such as actors, directors, and countries. The popularity scores of movies are used as the node importance.
dcterms:title: TMDB5K

dcterms:description: GA16K is a Geoscience academic knowledge graph from GAKG, containing about 16,000 entities such as papers, authors, and affiliations. The citation counts of papers are defined as the node importance.
dcterms:title: GA16K
